{"tid":1606543,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方SMS: 預計10月1日全港各區混亂及有未經警方批准的公眾活動","createTime":"2019-09-30T15:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T15:04:46.000Z","uid":297045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ebe7df626fa2f37fab4101415b0a9fae87db3707","tid":1606543,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/20190930_501860503708572_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F20190930_501860503708572_1.jpg&h=ee7041b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方今午（9月30日）又發出SMS呼籲，指明天全港各區預期<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>有未經批准的公眾活動</ins></span></strong>，可能引起混亂。 <br />\n<br />\n警方提醒市民請注意自身安全，留意警方新聞公布及社交媒體最新消息。 <br />\n<br />\n民陣計劃明日舉行的港島區集會及遊行，上周遭警方反對。公眾集會及遊行上訴委員會今早聆訊後，駁回民陣提出的上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/09-30-2019/56325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F09-30-2019%2F56325&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6rQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=67ca6877\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/09-30-2019/56325</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed1351a73030180fdcfa608186e55f74fc13330","tid":1606543,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"Telegram 預設訊息可以保護到手足性命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCXiwqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCXiwqP.png&h=5c04cb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星火 TG: @Abccbbc<br />\n612 TG: @ReliefFund612<br />\nPush"}]}